Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_continue_on_error(25.10)                timing_continue_on_error(25.10)

Name
       timing_continue_on_error

Syntax
        timing_continue_on_error

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       When  set to true, the software continues to process if an error occurs
       when any constraints are used, or during timing analysis, or when a li-
       brary is read. This global variable does not have any effect  on  other
       commands, except constraints or commands related to timing analysis.

       When  set to false, if an error occurs, during timing analysis, library
       reading, or defined constraints, the software stops processing and  ex-
       its.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

